snippet.title: SCP: Blackout Second Trailer
snippet.description:
This is the second trailer for  the upcoming VR/Desktop game SCP: Blackout. It comes out Dec. 14th. Thanks to The Volgun, his channel link below!
Discord group: https://discord.gg/zzXRpe2
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TheClassifiedX
Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/scpblackout/scp-blackout
Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/963400/SCP_Blackout/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/SCPBlackout/?view_public_for=267421327311940
TheVolgun's awesome channel for readings of SCPs: https://www.youtube.com/user/TheVolgun
